# Portfolio Review Trigger

When the user prompt contains the word `review` (case-insensitive), use the `portfolio-hiring-manager-review` skill.

Apply this especially for requests about:
- portfolio quality
- case study quality
- storytelling, visuals, coherence
- senior product designer hiring readiness

Default to the skill's structured output and always end with prioritized recommendations.
